title: Anne of the Island
creator: Lucy Maud Montgomery
description: Librivox public domain recording of Anne of the Island by Lucy Maud Montgomery. This is the continuing story of Anne Shirley and the third book in the Anne of Green Gables series. In it Anne attends Redmond College where she is studying for her BA. She has many trials and tribulations along the way, including some romance. In Anne of the Island the reader is also introduced to many new characters, that in the true sense of Anne are also "kindred spirits". (Summary from Wikipedia) M4B audiobook of complete book For more information or to volunteer, please visit librivox.org.
